Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
In my opinion, I beliebe that it is a good thing for students that the universities require the freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. When all freshman live together, they can become friends very easily. And this will be good for future study.